summary: 该插件用于检测畅捷通T-Plus系统的ajaxpro Ufida组件是否存在SQL注入漏洞，通过发送特定构造的请求并匹配响应内容来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect SQL injection vulnerabilities in the ajaxpro Ufida component of Ufida T-Plus system. It sends specially crafted requests and matches the response content to confirm the existence of the vulnerability.
